會嗯嗯腳。"},{"pid":"aec05bfce6d12d8e94709fa3bd3e85d96217b468","tid":1759823,"uid":62011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T01:01:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9b2112c1fe5db6d022ba745880e8073e1f36da24","tid":1759823,"uid":242291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T01:06:07.000Z","msg":"到英聯邦國家<br />\n港共死穴大部份班友都係英車加藉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6b23850110d1ba9299cbdc4c8c23bbaeab22536","tid":1759823,"uid":62011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T01:23:05.000Z","msg":"冇錯，英聯邦國家會行動，但需要時間。<br />\n<br />\n我哋香港要面對共產黨，佢好識玩政治。個戰場就算轉咗去議會，佢哋都可以控制到。"},{"pid":"89472be27543175c70020ed6198e4a35b5ff1a8b","tid":1759823,"uid":65024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"12b12c374c966fd1b9e0b95a492d2d5d70d3f1cf","tid":1759823,"uid":88517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T00:43:32.000Z","msg":"Be water act"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T01:23:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a596e1e545b1f3fd726f22592631e75523b42ea1","tid":1759823,"uid":283494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T01:25:15.000Z","msg":"立法之後就執法,不執行等於冇用"}]}